summary: I added four of my characters where I explore this universe called Tamriel.
descriptionHtml:
[size=5][color=#ffff00]I added four of my characters where I explore Skyrim.[/color]

[color=#00ff00][b]Manual Install - or install with some manager
==============
1. Extract the files to a temporary location such as the desktop.
2. Copy files to Skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/chargen/presets

Manual Uninstall
===============
1. Delete the files/folders associated with the mod.[/b]
